<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"/>
  <title>新问题已分配: ${issueId}</title>
</head>
<body>
<div>Dear ${name}</div>
<br/><br/>
<div>
  <span><strong>新问题已分配到你的账户，请注意查看</strong></span>
</div>
<br/><br/>
<div>
  <span>ID：</span>
  <span>${issueId}</span>
</div>
<div>
  <span>项目组：</span>
  <span>${groupName}</span>
</div>
<div>
  <span>项目：</span>
  <span>${projectName}</span>
</div>
<div>
  <span>模块：</span>
  <span>${moduleName}</span>
</div>
<div>
  <span>问题状态：</span>
  <span style="background-color: ${color}">${status}</span>
</div>
<div>
  <span>解决状态状态：</span>
  <span>${resolution}</span>
</div>
<div>
  <span>严重性：</span>
  <span style="color: ${severityColor}">${severity}</span>
</div>
<div>
  <span>优先级：</span>
  <span>${priority}</span>
</div>
<div>
  <span>提交人：</span>
  <span>${reportedBy}</span>
</div>
<div>
  <span>提交时间：</span>
  <span>${reportedAt}</span>
</div>
<div>
  <span>概述：</span>
  <span>${title}</span>
</div>
<br/><br/>
<div><span>这是系统生成的邮件，请勿回复</span></div>
</body>
</html>